OL,3,CEl Nino returns, raising fears of more
OL,4,Cextreme weather and higher food prices
OL,6,FThe UN has warned the world to prepare
OL,7,Ffor the imminent return of El Nino -
OL,8,Fthe powerful natural weather pattern
OL,9,Fwhich raises global temperatures and
OL,10,Fcan worsen rainfall. ITV News Science
OL,11,FCorrespondent Martin Stew explains
OL,13,FA naturally occurring climate pattern
OL,14,Fthat can influence weather across the
OL,15,Fglobe is returning, with forecasters
OL,16,Fwarning it could bring more extreme
OL,17,Fconditions over the coming year.
OL,26,@kD@FTw
