OL,3,CEl Nino returns, raising fears of more
OL,4,Cextreme weather and higher food prices
OL,6,FThe last El Nino, three years ago,
OL,7,Fcoincided with a series of extreme
OL,8,Fweather events. In the Amazon
OL,9,Frainforest, a record 44 million acres
OL,10,Fburned in devastating wildfires.
OL,12,FIn Canada, an area roughly equivalent
OL,13,Fto the size of England and Wales
OL,14,Fcombined was destroyed by fire,
OL,15,Freleasing an amount of carbon
OL,16,Fcomparable to India's annual emissions.
OL,26,@kD@FTwnD@OTw
