OL,3,CEl Nino returns, raising fears of more
OL,4,Cextreme weather and higher food prices
OL,6,FForecasters now believe there is a
OL,7,Fgrowing possibility that the next El
OL,8,FNino could be even stronger,
OL,9,Fincreasing the likelihood of heatwaves
OL,10,Fand episodes of extreme rainfall over
OL,11,Fthe next 12 months.
OL,13,FExperts also warn consumers could feel
OL,14,Fthe impact through higher food prices.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
