OL,3,CEl Nino returns, raising fears of more
OL,4,Cextreme weather and higher food prices
OL,6,FGlobal temperatures have continued to
OL,7,Frise over recent decades, driven by
OL,8,Fgreenhouse gas emissions.
OL,10,FThe United Nations Secretary-General
OL,11,Fhas warned that "El Nino conditions
OL,12,Fwill pour fuel on the fire of a
OL,13,Fwarming world."
